@startuml
|User|
start
: (1) Click on Create Account button;
|System|
: (2) Display form to create Employee's Account;
|User|
repeat: (3) Fill needed information;
: (4) Click Create button;
|System|
:Validate information;
backward: (5) Show error message;
repeat while (is data valid?) is (no) not (yes)
: (6) Create Employee Account;
stop
@enduml
